item.title: How can I load HD models on my 317 server?
item.dc:creator: @SGTCannon SGTCannon
item.description:
@SGTCannon wrote:

Mendorphins is right, this belongs in client help, but people often post for help with this in this section as well.

There are VERY few people that know how to actually load 508 and HD models on a 317 server, and they have basically vowed that they will never reveal how to do this. You can try PM’ing paladino though, he may have since changed his mind.
